{"title":"Satellite Photos of Middle Earth","link":"https://kottke.org/24/11/satellite-photos-of-middle-earth","date":1732723416000,"content":"\n        <p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/middle-earth-sat-01.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/middle-earth-sat-01.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/middle-earth-sat-01.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" alt=\"how Middle Earth would look from space\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/middle-earth-sat-02.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/middle-earth-sat-02.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/middle-earth-sat-02.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1300\" height=\"732\" alt=\"how Middle Earth would look from space\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/middle-earth-sat-03.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/middle-earth-sat-03.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/middle-earth-sat-03.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1300\" height=\"732\" alt=\"how Middle Earth would look from space\" /></p>\n\n<p>Using a 3D mapping engine, some Tolkien enthusiasts built <a href=\"https://forum.outerra.com/index.php?topic=2344.0\">a model of Middle Earth</a> that can be viewed from any angle, from the surface <a href=\"https://www.wired.com/2014/02/middle-earth-shots/\">to an orbital vantage point</a>.</p>\n\n<p>See also <a href=\"http://lotrproject.com/map/#zoom=3&amp;lat=-1692.5&amp;lon=1500&amp;layers=BTTTTT\">an interactive map of Middle Earth</a>.